OL,3,C'Reckless' driver sped away from
OL,4,Cpolice officers and crashed into
OL,5,Cfamily home
OL,7,FA "reckless" driver who sped away from
OL,8,Fpolice officers in Sussex and crashed
OL,9,Finto a family home has been
OL,10,Fdisqualified from driving for two
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FSamin Ahmed, 19, was driving at speeds
OL,14,Fof more than 130mph on the A2690
OL,15,FCoombe Valley Way in February this
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FRPU officer PC Lloyd Archer was on
OL,19,Fpatrol and saw Ahmed - who was driving
OL,20,Fhis father's BMW - overtaking three
OL,21,Fvehicles.
