OL,7,FThe police patrol activated its blue
OL,8,Flights, but Ahmed reached speeds of
OL,9,F110mph to evade officers.
OL,11,FHe then lost control of the vehicle
OL,12,Fand crashed into a house in Church
OL,13,FLane, Westfield, near Hastings.
OL,15,FPolice say a family had been in the
OL,16,Fliving room just minutes before the
OL,17,Fcrash.
