OL,3,C'Reckless' driver sped away from
OL,4,Cpolice officers and crashed into
OL,5,Cfamily home
OL,7,FIt left the building with structural
OL,8,Fproblems costing an estimated
OL,9,F#357,000, with the family unable to
OL,10,Flive in the property for several
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FAhmed's DNA was found on the car's
OL,14,Fairbag which showed he had been
OL,15,Fdriving the vehicle at the time of the
OL,16,Fcrash.
OL,18,FPC Archer said: "Ahmed's reckless
OL,19,Fdriving was appalling.
