OL,7,F"He risked his own life as well as the
OL,8,Fsafety of every other road user and
OL,9,Fresident, and is extremely lucky he
OL,10,Fdid not cause a fatality that night.
OL,12,F"We are determined to catch offenders
OL,13,Fand to prevent drivers causing harm to
OL,14,Fthemselves and innocent members of the
OL,15,Fpublic.
OL,17,F"So we are pleased that a dangerous
OL,18,Fdriver has been taken off our roads."
