OL,3,C'Reckless' driver sped away from
OL,4,Cpolice officers and crashed into
OL,5,Cfamily home
OL,7,FAhmed, formerly a security doorman, of
OL,8,FTavistock Road, Bromley, admitted
OL,9,Fdangerous driving and causing criminal
OL,10,Fdamage.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced to an 18-month
OL,13,Fsuspended prison sentence and was
OL,14,Fordered to complete 250 hours of
OL,15,Funpaid work.
OL,17,FHe was also ordered to complete 15
OL,18,FRehabilitation Activity Requirement
OL,19,Fsessions and to pay a #187 surcharge
OL,20,Fand #1,000 court costs.
